title: Seagate Expansion 5TB USB 3.0 Desktop Hard Drive - Speedy Unboxing from Argos
description:
This is quick unboxing of a Seagate Expansion USB 3.0 5TB desktop hard drive purchased from Argos for £129.99 today, I thought I would do a quick unboxing video - since I was un-boxing it anyway to use for backup and double-copies of my video archive and uploads, 4K video files can take up lots and of storage space quite fast.

Recorded Using A Samsung Galaxy SIII LTE.
